

=Bio=

Academic teacher, independent researcher and trainer.  She cooperates with a number of feminist organizations and informal groups working for more equal and ethical societies. She is a lecturer at the Gender Studies at the Jagiellonian University in Krakow and Polish Academy of Sciences in Warsaw. Currently - Postdoctoral Research Fellow in the Center for Transdisciplinary Gender Studies at the Humboldt-Universität zu Berlin. Her areas of scientific interest: feminist economics, new institutional economics, theory of commons.


